headline: Zacks Industry Outlook Highlights Brown and Brown, Marsh & McLennan, Arthur J. Gallagher and Willis Towers Watson Public
summary: Despite near-term headwinds, BRO, MMC, AJG, and WTW show resilience through M&A and tech-led growth.

headline: Marsh unveils insurance facility for data centre construction in Europe and UK
summary: The facility, Nimbus, offers up to €1bn ($1.16bn) in construction all-risks coverage and up to €350m for delay in start-up.
